name: Dreamcast Express Vol. 2
overview: Dreamcast Express Vol. 2 is a Japanese Sega Dreamcast demo disc released as part of the Dreamcast Express series. Videos - Pro Yakyuu Team o Tsukurou!, J.League Pro Soccer Club o Tsukurou! (Dreamcast), Frame Gride, Seaman: Kindan no Pet, Maken X, The King of Fighters: Dream Match 1999, Airforce Delta, D no Shokutaku 2, UnderCover AD2025 Kei VMU Data - Chou Hatsumei Boy Kani Pan: Bousou Roboto no Nazo!?, Climax Landers / Special - Tokyo Game Show '99 Spring, Interview with Hidekazu Yukawa & CM Making Disc 2 - Frame Gride Test Operation Disc (Tainkenban)
